author: Annum Masroor
title: Kansas City Royals Heading To World Series
text: Kansas City Royals Heading To World Series Annum Masroor Front Page Editor, The Huffington Post Posted: 10/24/2015 12:17 AM EDT LG Patterson via Getty Images The Kansas City Royals are headed to the World Series after winning the American League Championship Series with a 4-3 victory over the Toronto Blue Jays on Friday. The Royals won the ALCS in six games, and will face the New York Mets in Game 1 of the World Series on Tuesday.
